title.rendered: Mrs. Russian America 2021 in Los Angeles

content.rendered:
Mrs. Russian America 2021 in Los Angeles



24FashionTV is proud to be media partners with one of the largest Russian shows in the United States Mrs. Russian America.

This glamorous event will be held on April 29, 2021, in the Taglyan Complex in Los Angeles. The world will watch 20 beautiful ladies showcasing themselves and the best fashion collections of 2021 and competing for the main title Mrs. Russian America 2021.


For the second year in a row, this 2021 pageant will feature famous actors and show-business celebrities, top fashion designers, businessmen, athletes, and media will all be present that night. 

Cary Hiroyuki Tagawa, Eric Roberts, Bai Ling


The members of the all-star jury panel and special guests this year have grown to include more Hollywood celebrities. Master of ceremonies Alex Sparrow. From the founder and organizer of this pageant, Gennadiy Kotlyarchuk, the list this year will include:

Eric Roberts, Don Dragon Wilson, Olivier Gruner, Cynthia Rothrock, and many more.


On the schedule:

RED CARPET

BEAUTY PAGEANT

STAGE SHOW

AWARD CEREMONY

TOP DESIGNERS RUNWAY FASHION SHOW

24FashionTV will keep its viewers up to date on the results of the competition and the pageant surrounding it on its Amazon Fire TV and Roku TV channels as well as on its online app at https://24Fashion.tv 


24FashionTV is a new and quickly-growing project that includes the Worlds first Fashion Database, Social Media, and Television. Founders: Producer Victoria Unikel, Editor-In-Chief Galina Antonova, and Chief Technology Officer Gene Avakyan. 

This project is growing in popularity in the fashion world and beyond because its motto is to give a voice to all the designers, photographers, brands, and models of the world so that the people can make a better choice and express themselves for who they really are through the clothes they wear. Through Fashion.

Their editors will continue to keep an eye on 24FashionTVs growth and keep the viewers informed of their continued accomplishments.


original story


TAGS: 24 FASHION TV, LOS ANGELES, MRS. RUSSIAN AMERICAN, RUNWAY
